<a href="redirect.pl?http://www.amazon.com/gp/product/0764320742/ref=as_li_tl?ie=UTF8&camp=1789&creative=390957&creativeASIN=0764320742&linkCode=as2&tag=theinternetpi-20&linkId=Z72T2JLDLWNKE4TA">The Pinball Compendium 1970-1981</a>, page 75<br>
<a href="redirect.pl?http://www.amazon.com/gp/product/0451799666/ref=as_li_tl?ie=UTF8&camp=1789&creative=390957&creativeASIN=0451799666&linkCode=as2&tag=theinternetpi-20&linkId=Z72T2JLDLWNKE4TA">Pinball An Illustrated History</a>, page 63<br>
